import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-fetch-planet', templateUrl: './fetch-planet.component.html' }) export class FetchPlanetComponent { public planets: Planet[] = []; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + 'planet').subscribe(result => { this.planets = result; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface Planet { name: string; description: string; position: number; zodiacsigns: string; }
